      <head>Ferdinand Samuel Lischke</head>
      <div>

        <p>Berlin-based editor and publisher.</p>

        <p>Lischke was the editor of the <title level="j">Magazin für Kunst, Gewerbe und
            Musik</title> until c.1840. He was also a publisher, issuing music by Viotti, Dussek,
          Hummel and others. He published an edition of the Beethoven Piano Sonatas Op. 2, about
          which Schenker comments extensively in <ref cRef="entity-001741"><title level="j">Der
              Tonwille</title> 2</ref> (1921), pp. 37‒39 (Eng. transl, vol. I, pp. 83‒85).</p>
      </div>
